                "game-obj": "Traits",
                "game-id": "e5bbf09ab73401e1f1ef8cd208e061d9",
                "text": "An alchemical bomb combines volatile alchemical components that explode when the bomb hits a creature or object. Most alchemical bombs deal damage, though some produce other effects.",
                "classes": [
                    "trait"
                ]
            },
            {
                "name": "Consumable",
